data.description: Beautiful home nestled along a canal boasts a prime central location just minutes away from a boat ramp, vibrant community center, many dining options, and easy access to major highways. The inviting open floor plan adorned with ceramic tile flooring creates a seamless flow throughout. It features a spacious kitchen with a convenient bar, and additional dining and family room ideal for entertaining guests. Master bedroom offers a main bathroom with the ultimate in comfort: dual sinks, a separate shower, and a luxurious soaking tub. All appliances, including the washer and dryer, are included for added convenience.
